&lt;p&gt;We have an excellent opportunity to work as a part time fixed term consultant for a period of at least 3 months in one of our established CMHTs. The post would offer experience of working within Tower Hamlets Mental Health directorate and would suit someone interested in community based mental health care focused on recovery, partnership working across agencies and developing new models of mental health care delivery during the pandemic.&lt;/p&gt;
